tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    region_id UUID,
    population INT,
    age_group VARCHAR,
    ethnicity VARCHAR,
    income DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Voters (
    voter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_name VARCHAR,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    district_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	age INT,
	race VARCHAR(50),
	gender VARCHAR(10),
	ethnicity VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE district_data (
	district_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	district_name VARCHAR(50),
	total_population INT,
	demographic_data_id INT,
	FOREIGN KEY (demographic_data_id) REFERENCES demographic_data(id)
);

CREATE TABLE representation_data (
	representative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	district_id INT,
	representative_name VARCHAR(50),
	party_affiliation VARCHAR(20),
	FOREIGN KEY (district_id) REFERENCES district_data(district_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Redistricting_Demographics (
  state VARCHAR(50),
  city VARCHAR(50),
  population INT,
  ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
  age_group VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Voter_Information (
  voter_id INT,
  state VARCHAR(50),
  city VARCHAR(50),
  precinct_id INT,
  party_affiliation VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Census_Data (
  state VARCHAR(50),
  city VARCHAR(50),
  median_income DECIMAL,
  education_level VARCHAR(50),
  household_size INT
);

CREATE TABLE District_Representatives (
  district_id INT,
  representative_name VARCHAR(50),
  political_party VARCHAR(50),
  contact_email VARCHAR(50),
  contact_phone VARCHAR(20)
);
